1
00:00:47,730 --> 00:00:49,200
By His Majesty's oral decree,

2
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,660
Shen Mo, Registrar of the Penal Department,

3
00:00:50,660 --> 00:00:51,530
has shown merit in investigating cases

4
00:00:51,530 --> 00:00:52,900
and is observant of the finest details.

5
00:00:52,900 --> 00:00:55,060
He is hereby promoted to Vice Director of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

6
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:55,900
He shall take up the post immediately,

7
00:00:55,900 --> 00:00:56,830
assist the Director,

8
00:00:56,830 --> 00:00:58,800
and help observe anomalies in celestial phenomena.

9
00:00:58,800 --> 00:00:59,660
Respect this.

10
00:01:00,230 --> 00:01:01,900
Vice Director of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

11
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,600
I have shallow qualifications.

12
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:04,660
How can I be worthy?

13
00:01:04,660 --> 00:01:05,930
It is His Majesty's divine will.

14
00:01:05,930 --> 00:01:07,200
I dare not guess it.

15
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:08,730
The carriage is ready.

16
00:01:08,730 --> 00:01:11,160
Please depart immediately, Vice Director Shen.

17
00:01:11,160 --> 00:01:11,820
Your father

18
00:01:12,060 --> 00:01:15,860
is right under the Black Tower of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

19
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:17,500
Lord Qin, are you not going?

20
00:01:17,500 --> 00:01:19,300
I have other important matters.

21
00:01:29,660 --> 00:01:30,120
My lord.

22
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:33,200
We have arrived at the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

23
00:01:40,930 --> 00:01:42,860
The ninth floor of the Black Tower of the Imperial Astronomical Bureau.

24
00:01:42,860 --> 00:01:44,960
It is the central hub of the formations

25
00:01:44,960 --> 00:01:47,220
and also the entrance to the Dragon Vein.

26
00:01:47,860 --> 00:01:48,830
Vice Director Shen.

27
00:01:48,830 --> 00:01:49,830
Please follow me.

28
00:01:55,130 --> 00:01:56,600
Those veins are not still.

29
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:58,400
But faintly pulsating to a certain rhythm.

30
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,729
Like a living creature.

31
00:02:04,160 --> 00:02:05,230
Vice Director Shen.

32
00:02:05,230 --> 00:02:06,630
The Director ordered that

33
00:02:06,630 --> 00:02:07,660
since you are exhausted from the journey,

34
00:02:07,660 --> 00:02:08,919
you should rest first.

35
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:13,030
Someone will deliver three meals a day.

36
00:02:13,030 --> 00:02:14,330
The formations inside the tower are complex.

37
00:02:14,330 --> 00:02:15,700
Please do not wander around at night

38
00:02:15,700 --> 00:02:17,900
to avoid triggering the restrictions.

39
00:02:20,730 --> 00:02:23,329
Is my father, Shen Qingshan, inside the tower?

40
00:02:23,530 --> 00:02:24,460
I do not know.

41
00:02:37,230 --> 00:02:37,930
This room.

42
00:02:54,900 --> 00:02:55,900
The ninth floor.

43
00:02:57,900 --> 00:02:59,329
It's all blood.

44
00:02:59,400 --> 00:03:00,230
Whose blood?

45
00:03:00,930 --> 00:03:01,900
The Dragon Vein.

46
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:03,730
Drinks blood.

47
00:03:04,430 --> 00:03:06,200
It drank a lot.

48
00:03:24,829 --> 00:03:26,090
Blood crystal powder.

49
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:28,000
Mixed with cinnabar.

50
00:03:29,030 --> 00:03:30,290
Someone is warning me.

51
00:03:36,130 --> 00:03:37,200
Vice Director Shen.

52
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,660
The Director summons you.

53
00:03:40,760 --> 00:03:41,600
Lead the way.

54
00:04:00,730 --> 00:04:01,860
Vice Director Shen.

55
00:04:01,860 --> 00:04:02,760
You've had a hard journey.

56
00:04:02,760 --> 00:04:03,700
From today on,

57
00:04:03,860 --> 00:04:05,530
you will stay by my side.

58
00:04:05,860 --> 00:04:07,060
The truth about the Dragon Vein,

59
00:04:07,060 --> 00:04:07,800
I

60
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:09,200
will tell you slowly.

61
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:16,399
The jade pendant is the same.

62
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:19,860
This person.

63
00:04:20,100 --> 00:04:21,899
Who exactly is he?

64
00:04:21,899 --> 00:04:23,060
Some matters of the past,

65
00:04:23,060 --> 00:04:24,390
there is no need to rush.

66
00:04:24,500 --> 00:04:25,830
During tomorrow's morning lesson,

67
00:04:25,830 --> 00:04:28,630
I will explain the matters inside the tower to you.

68
00:04:28,730 --> 00:04:29,030
Yes.

69
00:04:29,030 --> 00:04:29,890
Lord Director.

70
00:04:30,100 --> 00:04:31,130
Very good.

71
00:04:31,760 --> 00:04:33,300
Go back to your room and rest first.
